://www.campuspecs.co.nz/appointment-enquiry/\" target=\"_blank\">book online</a>, to take advantage of this offer.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We were the first practice in New Zealand with a primary objective of offering eyecare and optical glasses for students, and helping you maximise your ability to learn has always been important to us. As the city’s only optometry practice offering first-rate eye care specifically tailored for tertiary students, we make it easy for you to take advantage of first rate eye care, benefits include extended opening hours and generous student discounts. We’re located just a short walk from both the University of Auckland and Auckland University of Technology. We are also official Eyecare partners with <a href=\"http://www.studentassist.co.nz/\" target=\"_blank\">Studentsafe.</a></p>\r\n<p>Our practice focuses on affordable fashion eyewear, with frames starting at $69. Many of our designer brands, including Chevrolet, XVO and Modem Girl are new to New Zealand. The broad range of frames, in diverse colours and materials mean you have a choice of over 350 options when selecting your new frames.</p>\r\n<p>Campuspecs has invested in leading edge technology so you’ll see clearly, we’re the first optometry practice in New Zealand to utilise the NIDEK Optical Path Difference Scanning System.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span class=\"categories\">Filed Under: <a href=\"http://www.campuspecs.co.nz/category/eye-care/\" rel=\"category tag\">EYE CARE</a>, <a href=\"http://www.campuspecs.co.nz/category/eye-examination/\" rel=\"category tag\">Eye Examination</a>, <a href=\"http://www.campuspecs.co.nz/category/eye-health/\" rel=\"category tag\">Eye Health</a>, <a href=\"http://www.campuspecs.co.nz/category/eyewear/\" rel=\"category tag\">Eyewear</a>, <a href=\"http://www.campuspecs.co.nz/category/news/\" rel=\"category tag\">News</a>, <a href=\"http://www.campuspecs.co.nz/category/uncategorized/\" rel=\"category tag\">Uncategorized</a></span> · <a href=